26
00:01:41,290 --> 00:01:42,770
Qian Jiayue.

27
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,950
Good for you.

28
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:46,840
I thought with your indecisive nature,

29
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,790
you'd wait till you're 30
to tell Xiao Han.

30
00:01:48,940 --> 00:01:49,920
- Ka Men.
- Turns out...

31
00:01:51,160 --> 00:01:52,120
You misunderstood.

32
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:56,040
Brother Xiao Han,

33
00:01:56,740 --> 00:01:58,520
do you know why I work so hard

34
00:01:58,980 --> 00:02:00,300
to get into

35
00:02:00,740 --> 00:02:01,780
No. 2 Middle School?

36
00:02:01,980 --> 00:02:02,820
I know.

37
00:02:07,490 --> 00:02:09,620
You didn't do well
in the Middle School Entrance Exam,

38
00:02:09,620 --> 00:02:11,190
and didn't make it into No. 2 Middle School.

39
00:02:11,390 --> 00:02:12,340
It's really unfortunate.

40
00:02:12,340 --> 00:02:13,180
I can feel it.

41
00:02:13,690 --> 00:02:16,240
You held onto this determination
for four years in middle school.

42
00:02:16,340 --> 00:02:18,420
You wanted to prove
you're not worse than me, right?

43
00:02:20,580 --> 00:02:21,660
No, that's not it.

44
00:02:21,980 --> 00:02:23,140
That's not what I meant.

45
00:02:23,140 --> 00:02:25,220
It's okay, being ambitious is good.

46
00:02:26,260 --> 00:02:27,980
Now you've entered No. 2 Middle School.

47
00:02:28,290 --> 00:02:29,900
In three years, let's see who does better

48
00:02:29,900 --> 00:02:31,260
in the College Entrance Exam.

49
00:02:32,300 --> 00:02:33,380
Brother Xiao Han,

50
00:02:33,740 --> 00:02:35,380
I actually wanted to say...

51
00:02:35,380 --> 00:02:36,780
- I...
- No need to be embarrassed.

52
00:02:36,780 --> 00:02:38,020
That's how learning works.

53
00:02:38,170 --> 00:02:40,300
Healthy competition leads to growth.

54
00:02:40,740 --> 00:02:41,580
Right?

55
00:02:41,820 --> 00:02:43,220
No, that's...

56
00:02:45,250 --> 00:02:46,410
You are both here.

57
00:02:47,740 --> 00:02:48,580
You found it.

58
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:49,780
Do you like it?

59
00:02:53,020 --> 00:02:55,060
It seems you don't like it much.

60
00:02:55,820 --> 00:02:56,660
No worries,

61
00:02:56,820 --> 00:02:58,620
I have a big gift for you.

62
00:02:59,180 --> 00:03:00,100
Surprise!

63
00:03:01,740 --> 00:03:02,620
What's this?

64
00:03:02,940 --> 00:03:03,780
Open it and see.

65
00:03:09,340 --> 00:03:10,380
My dear General!

66
00:03:10,380 --> 00:03:11,220
You...

67
00:03:11,940 --> 00:03:12,980
Mao Tou!

68
00:03:13,260 --> 00:03:14,980
How could you put a cricket in there?

69
00:03:17,980 --> 00:03:19,500
