70
00:03:19,940 --> 00:03:21,460
That's so crazy!

71
00:03:21,460 --> 00:03:22,300
Right?

72
00:03:23,660 --> 00:03:25,300
I really don't know what he was thinking.

73
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:27,140
His mind is always wandering.

74
00:03:28,540 --> 00:03:29,380
Sister,

75
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:31,500
I'm talking about you and Xiao Han.

76
00:03:32,500 --> 00:03:34,140
What do you want me to do?

77
00:03:34,140 --> 00:03:35,620
I've already told him,

78
00:03:35,690 --> 00:03:37,320
I entered the No. 2 Middle School for him.

79
00:03:38,140 --> 00:03:40,120
