with him academically.

80
00:03:41,220 --> 00:03:43,140
Then don't talk about studies with him.

81
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:45,220
Avoid triggering his competitive side.

82
00:03:45,620 --> 00:03:46,620
Enter his mind,

83
00:03:46,620 --> 00:03:47,620
and handle the rest.

84
00:03:48,300 --> 00:03:49,220
How do I do that?

85
00:04:05,340 --> 00:04:06,940
Aren't you good at folding origami stars?

86
00:04:07,140 --> 00:04:08,490
Give him this, then speak directly.

87
00:04:11,270 --> 00:04:14,470
♪Part the dark clouds in the sky♪

88
00:04:15,220 --> 00:04:17,100
