the theme song of Lotus Lantern.

92
00:04:22,540 --> 00:04:23,900
From Jeff Chang's

93
00:04:23,900 --> 00:04:25,180
"Love Is Only One Word".

94
00:04:25,540 --> 00:04:27,580
I wonder if you by the radio

95
00:04:27,580 --> 00:04:28,900
have found the one

96
00:04:28,900 --> 00:04:30,020
to say "love" to,

97
00:04:30,340 --> 00:04:32,220
and then to promise forever

98
00:04:32,300 --> 00:04:33,620
and to keep the faith.

99
00:04:34,110 --> 00:04:37,990
♪Hope you remember♪

100
00:04:38,210 --> 00:04:40,620
♪I'll always protect you♪

101
00:04:41,940 --> 00:04:44,980
Part the dark clouds in the sky.

102
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:49,540
It's as beautiful as blue velvet.

103
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:54,350
♪Shining brighter than stars♪

104
00:04:54,810 --> 00:04:57,890
♪Crossing mountains for you♪

105
00:04:58,570 --> 00:05:01,590
♪Ignoring the scenery♪

106
00:05:01,590 --> 00:05:04,980
(Yingmo Community)

107
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:09,140
♪Spreading messages through love's map♪

108
00:05:10,260 --> 00:05:11,980
It was filled up overnight.

109
00:05:12,860 --> 00:05:14,220
Couldn't sleep anyway.

110
00:05:14,220 --> 00:05:15,660
Might as well fold them all.

111
00:05:16,140 --> 00:05:16,980
Impressive.

112
00:05:17,740 --> 00:05:19,620
So, how will you tell Xiao Han this time?

113
00:05:21,140 --> 00:05:22,700
He definitely won't misunderstand again.

114
00:05:22,700 --> 00:05:24,240
Just talking about it makes me excited.

115
00:05:24,460 --> 00:05:25,900
Alright, go deliver it now.

116
00:05:27,300 --> 00:05:28,140
Now?

117
00:05:28,820 --> 00:05:29,860
Yes, go right now.

118
00:05:30,140 --> 00:05:30,980
As the saying goes,

119
00:05:31,420 --> 00:05:33,460
strike while the iron is hot,

120
00:05:33,460 --> 00:05:34,300
or lose momentum.

121
00:05:35,060 --> 00:05:37,540
You should tell him directly.

122
00:05:38,020 --> 00:05:39,580
Just receiving a jar of origami stars,

123
00:05:39,580 --> 00:05:40,820
doesn't really mean much.

124
00:05:41,180 --> 00:05:43,420
This isn't just any jar of origami stars.

125
00:05:43,740 --> 00:05:45,540
I've written codes inside it.

126
00:05:46,100 --> 00:05:46,940
Codes?

127
00:05:47,100 --> 00:05:47,940
Yes.

128
00:05:48,180 --> 00:05:50,380
There are 520 origami stars in total.

129
00:05:50,580 --> 00:05:52,220
Twenty of them are golden.

130
00:05:52,340 --> 00:05:53,620
The rest are blue.

131
00:05:53,980 --> 00:05:55,300
He just needs to open those twenty

132
00:05:55,300 --> 00:05:56,660
golden origami stars,

133
00:05:56,780 --> 00:05:57,620
and he'll find

134
00:05:57,700 --> 00:05:59,260
on each golden origami star,

135
00:05:59,260 --> 00:06:00,300
I've written a number.

136
00:06:00,740 --> 00:06:02,340
Once he arranged them by number,

137
00:06:02,580 --> 00:06:03,540
he'll discover

138
00:06:03,540 --> 00:06:04,860
it's a song's lyric.

139
00:06:05,380 --> 00:06:06,700
Song lyric?

140
00:06:07,380 --> 00:06:08,900
I first drafted them on paper,

141
00:06:08,900 --> 00:06:09,760
then copied onto them.

142
00:06:10,620 --> 00:06:12,420
Brother Xiao Han is smart,

143
00:06:12,620 --> 00:06:13,780
he'll surely understand,

144
00:06:15,700 --> 00:06:16,620
right?

145
00:06:29,820 --> 00:06:32,260
Stars are not just stars,

146
00:06:32,460 --> 00:06:34,460
there's a code within them.

147
00:06:34,660 --> 00:06:36,300
Isn't it much clearer now?

148
00:06:36,780 --> 00:06:37,740
Well...

149
00:06:41,060 --> 00:06:42,380
- Who is it?
- Wait, wait!

150
00:06:42,540 --> 00:06:43,380
It's me.

151
00:06:43,390 --> 00:06:44,820
Quickly, put it in Xiao Han's drawer!

152
00:06:45,580 --> 00:06:46,580
Xiao Han, Mao Tou,

153
00:06:46,740 --> 00:06:47,700
