154
00:06:47,820 --> 00:06:48,660
Why are you here?

155
00:06:48,660 --> 00:06:49,500
Brother Xiao Han.

156
00:06:55,060 --> 00:06:55,900
What's wrong?

157
00:06:58,500 --> 00:06:59,740
