160
00:07:03,210 --> 00:07:04,060
I have homework to do.

161
00:07:04,060 --> 00:07:05,540
Brother Xiao Han will watch me.

162
00:07:06,890 --> 00:07:08,060
The dictionary's in my drawer.

163
00:07:08,060 --> 00:07:08,900
Grab it yourself.

164
00:07:09,980 --> 00:07:10,900
- Don't!
- Don't!

165
00:07:14,180 --> 00:07:15,340
Don't what?

166
00:07:20,780 --> 00:07:22,180
Don't... don't…

167
00:07:24,020 --> 00:07:26,980
Don't be upset.

168
00:07:27,540 --> 00:07:29,740
I want you happy.

169
00:07:31,540 --> 00:07:32,440
Mao Tou,

170
00:07:32,460 --> 00:07:34,660
I learned a new song.

171
00:07:34,690 --> 00:07:35,980
- No...
- Can you listen for me?

172
00:07:35,980 --> 00:07:37,460
- What?
- Help me out here, okay?

173
00:07:39,620 --> 00:07:41,220
Is Ka Men alright?

174
00:07:41,460 --> 00:07:42,300
She...

175
00:07:43,020 --> 00:07:44,700
She should be okay.

176
00:07:45,140 --> 00:07:46,740
Maybe... Maybe...

177
00:07:46,740 --> 00:07:48,420
She's just excited about the new song.

178
00:07:51,820 --> 00:07:52,660
Brother Xiao Han,

179
00:07:52,660 --> 00:07:54,460
didn't you give me a pen last time?

180
00:07:55,220 --> 00:07:56,660
I've also prepared a gift for you,

181
00:07:56,660 --> 00:07:57,500
as a return gift.

182
00:07:57,500 --> 00:07:58,340
Really?

183
00:07:58,860 --> 00:08:00,020
I put it in your drawer.

184
00:08:00,540 --> 00:08:02,500
There's a little secret inside.

185
00:08:02,740 --> 00:08:04,660
You need to open it and look carefully.

186
00:08:05,140 --> 00:08:05,980
Alright.

187
00:08:07,620 --> 00:08:08,740
By the way, Brother Xiao Han,

188
00:08:08,740 --> 00:08:10,330
are you going to the Fuguilou Restaurant?

189
00:08:10,330 --> 00:08:11,180
Of course.

190
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:13,100
Then see you there.

191
00:08:15,220 --> 00:08:16,060
Ka Men.

192
00:08:16,060 --> 00:08:16,900
Coming.

193
00:08:18,580 --> 00:08:19,420
I...

194
00:08:19,900 --> 00:08:21,700
Your "distant travels",

195
00:08:21,700 --> 00:08:22,620
I feel like it's

196
00:08:22,620 --> 00:08:23,860
just a bit melancholic.

197
00:08:23,860 --> 00:08:25,660
But it lacks the feeling of wandering.

198
00:08:25,740 --> 00:08:27,540
I suggest you try experiencing it.

199
00:08:29,260 --> 00:08:30,180
Don't you think

200
00:08:30,380 --> 00:08:31,740
they're acting a bit odd today?

201
00:08:32,420 --> 00:08:33,300
Really odd.

202
00:08:41,540 --> 00:08:42,540
What are you looking for?

203
00:08:42,620 --> 00:08:44,460
Jiayue said she prepared
a return gift for me,

204
00:08:44,940 --> 00:08:46,020
but I can't find it.

205
00:08:46,180 --> 00:08:47,020
A return gift?

206
00:08:48,100 --> 00:08:49,500
Is there one for me too?

207
00:08:50,180 --> 00:08:51,020
Let me check.

208
00:08:53,780 --> 00:08:54,620
Wait.

209
00:08:56,260 --> 00:08:57,140
Did you hear that?

210
00:08:58,300 --> 00:08:59,140
Hear what?

211
00:08:59,180 --> 00:09:00,020
General's chirping.

212
00:09:00,020 --> 00:09:00,900
Didn't you hear it?

213
00:09:02,260 --> 00:09:03,580
The sound of General.

214
00:09:10,020 --> 00:09:10,860
Got it.

215
00:09:11,660 --> 00:09:12,620
Leave it to me.

216
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,240
When I, Zhang Qiming, handle things,

217
00:09:14,660 --> 00:09:15,860
you can absolutely trust me.

218
00:09:17,820 --> 00:09:18,660
Little imp,

219
00:09:18,810 --> 00:09:19,660
move faster.

220
00:09:19,660 --> 00:09:20,620
Are you sewing inside?

221
00:09:21,580 --> 00:09:23,100
Hold the baijiu steady, don't spill it.

222
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:27,820
The hairstyle

223
00:09:28,260 --> 00:09:29,340
must be neat.

224
00:09:38,460 --> 00:09:42,500
(Fuguilou Restaurant)

225
00:09:42,500 --> 00:09:43,340
Wait a moment.

226
00:09:44,300 --> 00:09:45,740
Parking fee is twenty.

227
00:09:45,860 --> 00:09:47,620
That expensive? It's not a train.

228
00:09:48,300 --> 00:09:49,140
Ten.

229
00:09:49,740 --> 00:09:50,580
That won't do.

230
00:09:50,780 --> 00:09:51,900
Just grabbing a bite.

231
00:09:51,980 --> 00:09:52,820
The kid has got into

232
00:09:52,820 --> 00:09:54,300
a prestigious high school.

233
00:09:54,300 --> 00:09:55,150
Impressive, huh?

234
00:09:55,160 --> 00:09:57,420
(Congratulations to Qian Jiayue
for getting into No. 2 Middle School)

235
00:09:57,420 --> 00:09:58,580
Ten yuan.

236
00:09:59,040 --> 00:09:59,940
Come on.

237
00:09:59,940 --> 00:10:00,940
Let's celebrate together.

238
00:10:02,580 --> 00:10:03,420
Ten yuan.

239
00:10:03,500 --> 00:10:04,540
Fine, ten yuan it is.

240
00:10:05,620 --> 00:10:06,660
Give him ten yuan.

241
00:10:06,660 --> 00:10:08,260
I don't have change, only bills.

242
00:10:11,380 --> 00:10:12,340
Here you are.

243
00:10:12,900 --> 00:10:14,620
Sir. Issue an invoice, thank you.

244
00:10:15,390 --> 00:10:16,540
- Hold on.
- Thanks, thanks.

245
00:10:17,980 --> 00:10:19,380
Congratulations to Qian Jiayue

246
00:10:19,380 --> 00:10:20,840
for getting into No. 2 Middle School.

247
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:21,860
What about you, little imp?

248
00:10:21,860 --> 00:10:23,380
If we can put up a sign
like this next year,

249
00:10:23,380 --> 00:10:24,860
not to mention Fuguilou Restaurant,

250
00:10:24,860 --> 00:10:26,100
I can make the Oriental Pearl

251
00:10:26,100 --> 00:10:27,540
Revolving Restaurant revolve for you.

252
00:10:27,740 --> 00:10:29,220
What's good about No. 2 Middle School?

253
00:10:30,420 --> 00:10:32,140
You really like to boast, don't you?

254
00:10:32,260 --> 00:10:33,940
Focus your cricket fighting energy

255
00:10:33,940 --> 00:10:34,900
on studying instead.

256
00:10:35,460 --> 00:10:36,340
If you were

257
00:10:36,500 --> 00:10:37,500
half as good as them,

258
00:10:37,500 --> 00:10:38,620
I'd be very thankful.

259
00:10:39,020 --> 00:10:39,940
If you were

260
00:10:39,940 --> 00:10:41,300
half as supportive as their parents,

261
00:10:41,300 --> 00:10:42,380
I'd also be thankful.

262
00:10:42,380 --> 00:10:44,060
Traveling for work
and drinking all the time,

263
00:10:44,060 --> 00:10:45,020
never home.

264
00:10:45,220 --> 00:10:46,380
I feel like an orphan,

265
00:10:46,380 --> 00:10:47,340
relying on others for meals.

266
00:10:47,340 --> 00:10:49,100
Have I left you undisciplined for too long?

267
00:10:49,100 --> 00:10:49,940
I'll give you a slap now!

268
00:10:50,980 --> 00:10:51,900
Here's your invoice.

269
00:10:53,260 --> 00:10:54,100
Thank you.

270
00:10:55,690 --> 00:10:56,940
Stop playing? Get inside.

271
00:10:58,740 --> 00:10:59,740
Look at you, such a mess.

272
00:11:05,340 --> 00:11:12,340
(Congratulations to Jiayue, Wanqing and Han
for getting into No. 2 Middle School)

273
00:11:12,340 --> 00:11:13,180
Director,

274
00:11:13,740 --> 00:11:15,300
would you like some fresh juice?

275
00:11:15,300 --> 00:11:16,140
Sure, sure.

276
00:11:16,580 --> 00:11:18,340
It's very sweet.

277
00:11:18,740 --> 00:11:19,900
Just a little, just a little.

278
00:11:23,060 --> 00:11:24,060
Brother Xiao Han,

279
00:11:24,580 --> 00:11:25,580
did you notice something?

280
00:11:25,980 --> 00:11:26,900
Notice what?

281
00:11:29,340 --> 00:11:30,260
Look at this.

282
00:11:31,340 --> 00:11:32,180
This?

283
00:11:32,900 --> 00:11:33,740
What is it?

284
00:11:35,830 --> 00:11:36,670
This

285
