- No, I haven't.
- No? Thank you.

572
00:22:16,740 --> 00:22:17,980
Qian Jiayue!

573
00:22:18,620 --> 00:22:19,540
You go this way,

574
00:22:19,540 --> 00:22:20,380
I'll go that way.

575
00:22:21,900 --> 00:22:22,820
Baby!

576
00:22:28,660 --> 00:22:29,500
She's back.

577
00:22:31,540 --> 00:22:32,380
How was it?

578
00:22:32,820 --> 00:22:33,820
Did you find her?

579
00:22:34,420 --> 00:22:36,020
Everyone's gone now.

580
00:22:36,340 --> 00:22:37,420
They've all left.

581
00:22:38,820 --> 00:22:40,380
So much food was left uneaten.

582
00:22:40,760 --> 00:22:41,660
It can be packed.

583
00:22:41,660 --> 00:22:42,700
I'll settle the bill.

584
00:22:42,700 --> 00:22:44,590
- There's a lot going on.
- Where are you going?

585
00:22:44,660 --> 00:22:45,740
I've already paid the bill.

586
00:22:45,790 --> 00:22:46,890
The most important thing now

587
00:22:47,030 --> 00:22:48,180
is to find Jiayue.

588
00:22:50,470 --> 00:22:52,120
I can't find her.

589
00:22:54,310 --> 00:22:55,740
Can't find her.

590
00:22:56,220 --> 00:22:57,700
Come, sit down.

591
00:22:58,080 --> 00:22:58,970
Don't worry.

592
00:22:59,140 --> 00:23:00,020
Let's not rush.

593
00:23:04,260 --> 00:23:05,260
I...

594
00:23:05,260 --> 00:23:06,700
I really have to say.

595
00:23:06,700 --> 00:23:08,260
You were a bit much earlier.

596
00:23:08,540 --> 00:23:10,140
She has grown up, you know?

597
00:23:10,140 --> 00:23:11,460
Time quietly passes.

598
00:23:11,460 --> 00:23:12,500
Everyone has secrets now.

599
00:23:12,500 --> 00:23:14,020
Why dig through the trash

600
00:23:14,020 --> 00:23:15,300
and expose her secrets

601
00:23:15,300 --> 00:23:16,700
in front of everyone?

602
00:23:17,060 --> 00:23:17,900
Alright, alright.

603
00:23:19,060 --> 00:23:20,100
Stop crying.

604
00:23:21,100 --> 00:23:22,390
It's a mother and daughter thing,

605
00:23:22,940 --> 00:23:24,380
no grudges overnight.

606
00:23:24,500 --> 00:23:25,660
You all know that

607
00:23:26,700 --> 00:23:27,540
my baby

608
00:23:27,900 --> 00:23:29,860
wasn't raised by me, right?

609
00:23:29,860 --> 00:23:32,940
Back then, I was in Jiangxi,
working in the countryside.

610
00:23:33,420 --> 00:23:34,980
We just wanted to

611
00:23:35,540 --> 00:23:37,660
send her to Shanghai early.

612
00:23:37,940 --> 00:23:40,340
Shanghai had better living conditions,

613
00:23:40,340 --> 00:23:42,300
- good for the kid.
- Yes.

614
00:23:42,380 --> 00:23:44,620
I would do anything to get her

615
00:23:44,620 --> 00:23:45,820
to Shanghai.

616
00:23:45,820 --> 00:23:48,700
I remember the day
I had to return to Jiangxi.

617
00:23:58,100 --> 00:23:58,940
Baby,

618
00:24:00,020 --> 00:24:01,220
I promise you,

619
00:24:02,140 --> 00:24:05,100
I will be back next year,

620
00:24:05,100 --> 00:24:05,940
okay?

621
00:24:06,220 --> 00:24:08,220
A year goes by quickly.

622
00:24:10,340 --> 00:24:12,700
Xiu'e, time to leave.

623
00:24:14,090 --> 00:24:14,980
Baby...

624
00:24:38,860 --> 00:24:41,260
I've regretted it since then.

625
00:24:41,580 --> 00:24:44,020
I've regretted it to this day.

626
00:24:44,020 --> 00:24:45,980
I shouldn't have left her in Shanghai.

627
00:24:45,980 --> 00:24:47,580
I should have raised her myself.

628
00:24:50,740 --> 00:24:51,580
Alright,

629
00:24:52,420 --> 00:24:54,380
stop thinking about this now.

630
00:24:54,540 --> 00:24:55,900
Back then, you didn't know

631
00:24:55,900 --> 00:24:57,180
when you could return to Shanghai.

632
00:24:57,180 --> 00:24:58,460
You just made

633
00:24:58,700 --> 00:25:00,300
the right choice for the kid.

634
00:25:00,380 --> 00:25:01,260
Yes, indeed.

635
00:25:01,420 --> 00:25:02,260
My baby,

636
00:25:02,340 --> 00:25:03,260
let me tell you,

637
00:25:03,260 --> 00:25:05,140
isn't close to me at all.

638
00:25:05,860 --> 00:25:08,420
She's only close to my mom.

639
00:25:09,140 --> 00:25:11,100
She doesn't tell me anything.

640
00:25:11,300 --> 00:25:12,820
I have no other choice.

641
00:25:12,820 --> 00:25:15,340
I just have to search this and that.

642
00:25:15,340 --> 00:25:17,500
I just want to understand her more.

643
00:25:17,740 --> 00:25:19,620
I want to make it up to her, right?

644
00:25:19,620 --> 00:25:20,460
If you

645
00:25:20,860 --> 00:25:22,220
want to be good to the kid,

646
00:25:23,140 --> 00:25:25,020
you should do it
in a way she accepts.

647
00:25:25,020 --> 00:25:25,860
Right?

648
00:25:26,220 --> 00:25:27,060
Otherwise,

649
00:25:27,500 --> 00:25:28,860
you'll just push her further away.

650
00:25:32,480 --> 00:25:33,370
True.

651
00:25:34,660 --> 00:25:36,660
Pei, what you said makes sense.

652
00:25:37,150 --> 00:25:37,990
Right?

653
00:25:40,630 --> 00:25:41,470
Wait.

654
00:25:42,880 --> 00:25:43,790
My baby said,

655
00:25:44,140 --> 00:25:46,280
I took advantage
even for two bowls of wontons.

656
00:25:47,520 --> 00:25:48,410
You told her that?

657
00:25:51,950 --> 00:25:52,980
The thing is...

658
00:25:54,140 --> 00:25:56,420
I was just joking with you.

659
00:25:56,420 --> 00:25:59,200
Why do you tell my daughter everything?

660
00:25:59,200 --> 00:26:00,520
I was kidding.

661
00:26:01,700 --> 00:26:04,380
I was kidding too, do you believe me?

662
00:26:07,420 --> 00:26:09,340
(Jiale Wontons)

663
00:26:10,140 --> 00:26:10,980
Mom.

664
00:26:11,460 --> 00:26:12,540
Did you find Qian Jiayue?

665
00:26:13,820 --> 00:26:15,100
Not yet, still looking.

666
00:26:15,100 --> 00:26:15,940
You're back.

667
00:26:16,390 --> 00:26:17,230
Let me tell you,

668
00:26:17,700 --> 00:26:18,900
Chen Xiu'e really

669
00:26:18,900 --> 00:26:20,340
overdid it this time,

670
00:26:20,580 --> 00:26:21,420
she went too far.

671
00:26:21,420 --> 00:26:23,350
What meant to be poetry recitals,

672
00:26:23,360 --> 00:26:24,550
ended up with lyric reading.

673
00:26:24,560 --> 00:26:25,940
So embarrassing!

674
00:26:26,620 --> 00:26:27,460
Exactly.

675
00:26:27,660 --> 00:26:29,160
What kid likes that?

676
00:26:29,160 --> 00:26:30,540
- Yeah.
- I like that.

677
00:26:32,740 --> 00:26:33,860
Qian Jiayue's mom,

678
00:26:34,110 --> 00:26:35,370
doing this and that,

679
00:26:35,510 --> 00:26:36,680
whether it's right or wrong,

680
00:26:37,100 --> 00:26:38,250
it's all out of loving her

681
00:26:38,250 --> 00:26:39,250
and being proud of her.

682
00:26:40,340 --> 00:26:41,740
I also got into No. 2 Middle School.

683
00:26:42,660 --> 00:26:44,640
I feel like no one is proud of me.

684
00:26:50,610 --> 00:26:51,730
She was talking about you.

685
00:26:54,720 --> 00:26:56,300
Never proud of your daughter.

686
00:26:57,980 --> 00:26:58,820
I...

687
00:26:59,660 --> 00:27:03,780
(Mao Tou's Home - Idle People Keep Away)

688
00:27:03,780 --> 00:27:04,620
Brother Xiao Han.

689
00:27:05,220 --> 00:27:06,220
I'm out of ink again.

690
00:27:07,060 --> 00:27:09,260
Brother Xiao Han, how's Sister Jiayue?

691
00:27:09,660 --> 00:27:11,300
She's fine now, already back home.

692
00:27:11,300 --> 00:27:12,420
I mean, seriously,

693
00:27:12,420 --> 00:27:14,500
why was she so angry with Godmother?

694
00:27:15,020 --> 00:27:16,220
And I find her quite odd.

695
00:27:16,700 --> 00:27:18,500
If she wanted to give me a jar,
just give it.

696
00:27:18,540 --> 00:27:19,980
Why put so many origami stars inside?

697
00:27:19,980 --> 00:27:21,580
What's the point of that?

698
00:27:22,440 --> 00:27:24,030
And there's a note saying something like,

699
00:27:24,380 --> 00:27:26,180
"Stars are not just stars,

700
00:27:26,340 --> 00:27:27,900
there's a code within them."

701
00:27:28,910 --> 00:27:31,390
I don't get it. Maybe she's playing
a guessing game.

702
00:27:32,620 --> 00:27:35,900
The origami stars I gave you,
have you checked them?

703
00:27:48,380 --> 00:27:49,960
Actually, I wanted to say,

704
00:27:50,260 --> 00:27:51,180
this

705
00:27:51,180 --> 00:27:52,740
looks like a red date,

706
00:27:52,940 --> 00:27:55,380
but the key is the glutinous rice inside.

707
00:28:00,580 --> 00:28:02,580
Our baby is really thoughtful.

708
00:28:02,740 --> 00:28:04,060
She gave a return gift

709
00:28:04,060 --> 00:28:05,020
with a code.

710
00:28:05,100 --> 00:28:07,260
What do these numbers mean?

711
00:28:07,260 --> 00:28:08,620
One, two, three, four, five...

712
00:28:18,540 --> 00:28:20,300
"Love Is Only One Word".

713
00:28:21,820 --> 00:28:23,500
(A certain column of words in the lyrics)

714
00:28:30,580 --> 00:28:31,500
Brother Xiao Han,

715
00:28:31,940 --> 00:28:33,730
do you know why I work so hard

716
00:28:34,060 --> 00:28:35,580
to get into

717
00:28:36,100 --> 00:28:36,980
No. 2 Middle School?

718
00:28:41,820 --> 00:28:42,660
Nice shot!

719
00:28:49,260 --> 00:28:50,950
- You're back.
- Honey, the baby's back?

720
00:28:50,950 --> 00:28:51,980
- Don't rush, don't rush.
- Baby...

721
00:28:51,980 --> 00:28:52,820
Wait, wait.

722
00:28:52,860 --> 00:28:53,820
She's inside.

723
00:28:54,160 --> 00:28:56,020
Let her have some time alone.

724
00:29:03,280 --> 00:29:04,180
Baby,

725
00:29:04,580 --> 00:29:05,840
Granny is coming in.

726
00:29:12,020 --> 00:29:13,240
It's okay, don't worry.

727
00:29:16,010 --> 00:29:18,050
I made you some pumpkin porridge.

728
00:29:18,060 --> 00:29:18,900
Would you like some?

729
00:29:20,210 --> 00:29:21,370
It's a bit hot now.

730
00:29:21,940 --> 00:29:22,860
Let it cool down first.

731
00:29:29,380 --> 00:29:30,780
Don't be upset.

732
00:29:31,110 --> 00:29:32,670
Your mom is just like that,

733
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:33,810
you know it.

734
00:29:34,040 --> 00:29:36,780
She always needs to be
the center of attention.

735
00:29:37,490 --> 00:29:39,090
Even when she's wrong,

736
00:29:39,100 --> 00:29:40,250
she never admits it.

737
00:29:40,820 --> 00:29:41,660
Exactly.

738
00:29:43,540 --> 00:29:44,380
But

739
00:29:44,910 --> 00:29:46,420
for someone like her,

740
00:29:46,900 --> 00:29:47,900
do you know

741
00:29:48,280 --> 00:29:51,460
what made her truly let go of her pride?

742
00:29:52,160 --> 00:29:53,200
What's the matter?

743
00:29:54,570 --> 00:29:58,500
That year, bringing you
from Jiangxi to Shanghai,

744
00:29:58,500 --> 00:29:59,900
she asked me for help.

745
00:30:03,140 --> 00:30:04,130
Your mom

746
00:30:04,310 --> 00:30:06,170
settled in Jiangxi early on.

747
00:30:06,300 --> 00:30:08,290
Life was really tough then.

748
00:30:09,380 --> 00:30:11,020
Then she met your dad.

749
00:30:12,790 --> 00:30:14,610
Maybe your mom thought

750
00:30:15,050 --> 00:30:17,080
she couldn't let you suffer with them.

751
00:30:17,260 --> 00:30:18,390
That's why she decided

752
00:30:18,710 --> 00:30:20,300
to send you back to Shanghai.

753
00:30:21,340 --> 00:30:22,180
Twenty years.

754
00:30:23,230 --> 00:30:24,070
Twenty years,

755
00:30:24,080 --> 00:30:25,190
never once did your mom

756
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:27,060
yield to me.

757
00:30:27,500 --> 00:30:28,420
That afternoon,

758
00:30:29,980 --> 00:30:32,910
she said so many nice things to me.

759
00:30:37,320 --> 00:30:38,520
Her pride,

760
00:30:39,110 --> 00:30:40,010
she completely let go.

761
00:30:43,910 --> 00:30:44,890
So Baby,

762
00:30:45,280 --> 00:30:46,120
you

763
00:30:46,410 --> 00:30:48,660
can say she doesn't keep promises.

764
00:30:49,210 --> 00:30:50,330
You can say she

765
00:30:50,790 --> 00:30:51,900
peeks at your diary.

766
00:30:52,100 --> 00:30:53,140
But remember one thing.

767
00:30:54,980 --> 00:30:56,800
You must never say your mom

768
00:30:57,850 --> 00:30:59,660
doesn't care about you.

769
00:31:00,940 --> 00:31:01,780
Got it?

770
00:31:05,420 --> 00:31:06,260
Come.

771
00:31:07,180 --> 00:31:08,020
Hurry up.

772
00:31:21,100 --> 00:31:22,040
Tasty, right?

773
00:32:01,030 --> 00:32:03,500
♪Little girl♪

774
00:32:03,700 --> 00:32:06,950
♪You've let your hair grow long♪

775
00:32:08,010 --> 00:32:12,310
♪You've loosened the hand
that tightly held mine♪

776
00:32:14,870 --> 00:32:17,290
♪No longer do you♪

777
00:32:17,450 --> 00:32:20,790
♪Whisper in my ear♪

778
00:32:21,510 --> 00:32:28,410
♪Little girl, don't be afraid♪

779
00:32:33,260 --> 00:32:34,700
One, two, three.

780
00:32:35,330 --> 00:32:37,730
Baby, can I come in?

781
00:32:38,320 --> 00:32:40,770
I just want to give you something.

782
00:32:40,770 --> 00:32:42,040
I'll leave after I put it down.

783
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:44,690
I promise I won't bother you, okay?

784
00:32:47,900 --> 00:32:48,740
Okay.

785
00:33:02,420 --> 00:33:05,400
Baby, this is for your computer.

786
00:33:05,830 --> 00:33:07,280
What are you doing?

787
00:33:08,110 --> 00:33:09,860
I said I don't need a computer.

788
00:33:10,080 --> 00:33:11,890
I know you're thoughtful.

789
00:33:12,940 --> 00:33:13,800
But,

790
00:33:14,860 --> 00:33:16,500
I've thought it over.

791
00:33:17,020 --> 00:33:17,970
It's just that...

792
00:33:19,330 --> 00:33:20,830
For your studies,

793
00:33:20,840 --> 00:33:22,340
I will always support you.

794
00:33:23,120 --> 00:33:24,010
Don't worry,

795
00:33:24,010 --> 00:33:25,820
I promise to keep my word this time.

796
00:33:28,860 --> 00:33:30,350
To buy a computer,

797
00:33:30,350 --> 00:33:31,820
it's fine if you don't want me to go.

798
00:33:31,820 --> 00:33:33,060
I won't go, I won't go.

799
00:33:33,390 --> 00:33:36,190
I'll call your Aunt Guan, and ask Mao Tou

800
00:33:36,200 --> 00:33:38,470
and Xiao Han to join you, alright?

801
00:33:38,470 --> 00:33:39,380
All the money,

802
00:33:39,900 --> 00:33:40,940
where did you get it from?

803
00:33:41,160 --> 00:33:42,540
About the money,

804
00:33:42,940 --> 00:33:44,550
you don't need to worry.

805
00:33:44,550 --> 00:33:45,960
I have my ways.

806
00:33:45,960 --> 00:33:48,060
If you don't tell me, I won't take it.

807
00:33:52,620 --> 00:33:53,730
Well...

808
00:34:16,940 --> 00:34:18,220
The IOU is ready.

809
00:34:18,580 --> 00:34:19,420
Don't worry.

810
00:34:19,620 --> 00:34:21,340
After my term deposit matures next year,

811
00:34:21,340 --> 00:34:23,500
I'll repay you with interest.

812
00:34:25,240 --> 00:34:26,940
No need to write an IOU.

813
00:34:26,940 --> 00:34:28,140
That money

814
00:34:28,390 --> 00:34:30,660
is from Baby's two uncles.

815
00:34:31,420 --> 00:34:33,640
Take the computer as a gift from them.

816
00:34:34,170 --> 00:34:35,300
That's not right.

817
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:36,980
Even brothers settle accounts clearly.

818
00:34:37,140 --> 00:34:38,180
Let's keep things separate.

819
00:34:39,250 --> 00:34:41,750
I'll buy my daughter's computer myself.

820
00:34:42,740 --> 00:34:44,420
(Term Deposit Receipt: Fifteen Thousand Yuan)
This

821
00:34:44,420 --> 00:34:45,420
is a deposit.

822
00:34:46,500 --> 00:34:47,600
But don't worry,

823
00:34:47,610 --> 00:34:48,640
I have money.

824
00:34:48,650 --> 00:34:50,220
I have it in the bank.

825
00:34:50,400 --> 00:34:52,140
When it matures, I'll withdraw it.

826
00:34:52,140 --> 00:34:54,100
I'll repay your granny with interest.

827
00:34:57,340 --> 00:34:58,580
Also,

828
00:34:58,900 --> 00:35:01,220
I reflected on myself.

829
00:35:02,140 --> 00:35:03,260
Regarding last time,

830
00:35:04,500 --> 00:35:05,500
it was my fault.

831
00:35:05,700 --> 00:35:08,740
I shouldn't have gone through your things.

832
00:35:10,980 --> 00:35:12,780
I promise you this.

833
00:35:13,140 --> 00:35:14,780
In the future, without your permission,

834
00:35:14,790 --> 00:35:16,500
I'll never enter your room.

835
00:35:18,340 --> 00:35:20,740
Even if I come to clean,

836
00:35:20,740 --> 00:35:22,620
I won't go through your things.

837
00:35:24,380 --> 00:35:25,220
Is that okay?

838
00:35:25,220 --> 00:35:26,060
So,

839
00:35:26,660 --> 00:35:27,940
can you forgive me?

840
00:35:39,100 --> 00:35:40,180
Also, I

841
00:35:42,440 --> 00:35:44,180
shouldn't have snapped at you

842
00:35:44,500 --> 00:35:45,620
in front of them.

843
00:35:46,540 --> 00:35:47,420
Sorry.

844
00:35:54,100 --> 00:35:54,940
Well...

845
00:35:55,020 --> 00:35:56,290
Baby, keep the money safe.

846
00:35:56,300 --> 00:35:57,980
I'll head out now.

847
00:36:01,420 --> 00:36:03,220
Okay, I'm leaving.

848
00:36:03,820 --> 00:36:05,020
I'm off.

849
00:36:07,820 --> 00:36:09,420
Baby, one more thing.

850
00:36:09,540 --> 00:36:10,570
About this money,

851
00:36:10,570 --> 00:36:11,900
make sure you keep it well.

852
00:36:12,060 --> 00:36:13,580
Anyway, you three kids,

853
00:36:13,990 --> 00:36:16,220
be careful out there.

854
00:36:17,550 --> 00:36:19,680
I'll stop talking. I'm leaving now.

855
00:36:20,360 --> 00:36:21,200
Mom.

856
00:36:22,780 --> 00:36:23,840
Come with us.

857
